title: (Fri Early Bird) Our Old Intern Lexie Stops by After Making It Big + Fun Fact Friday: The Creepy Backstory of A Popular Song
itunes:title: (Fri Early Bird) Our Old Intern Lexie Stops by After Making It Big + Fun Fact Friday: The Creepy Backstory of A Popular Song
description:
Lexie Hayden stops by. She used to be an intern for our show back in 2014 and now just made her TV debut on an MTV reality show. In Fun Fact Friday, Amy shares things you may not know about Froot Loops, Chuck. E Cheese and the creepy backstory of a very popular song.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
